OL,1,D]S737{kkkc5FNumber struggling to pay   
OL,2,D]S555{jjj25Fbills soars by 40%         
OL,3,D]Suuu{rrzq5F                           
OL,4,T#######################################
OL,5, The number of people struggling to pay 
OL,6, their bills and debts has risen by     
OL,7, nearly 40%, the UK's financial         
OL,8, regulator has said.                    
OL,10,FThe Financial Conduct Authority (FCA)  
OL,11,Fsaid 10.9 million adults were          
OL,12,Fstruggling in this way in January - 3.1
OL,13,Fmillion more people than in May 2022.  
OL,15,FAn FCA survey found 11% of adults      
OL,16,Fmissed a bill or loan payment in at    
OL,17,Fleast three of the previous six months.
OL,19,FThe regulator has encouraged people    
OL,20,Fstruggling to ask lenders for help.    
